==Chinese==
===[[wikipedia:Taiwanese Mandarin|Taiwanese Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: yī cù kě jī

===Etymology===
Literally: able to approach within one step

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[蹴]][[可]][[幾]]'''

# to reach the goal in one step; do it all in one single day
#: ''[[學習]][[過程]][[絕非]]'''一蹴可幾''，[[甭]][[想]][[一次]][[就]][[記住]][[全部]].''
#: ''The learning process is not such that you can just '''do it all in one single day'''.  Don't think that you will be able to remember everything in one sitting.''

===Alternate forms===
